<refsect1 id="GdvIndicator.description" role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para><link linkend="GdvIndicator"><type>GdvIndicator</type></link> is an object-class, that displays an indicator for any given
value on a single axis.</para>
<refsect2><title>CSS nodes</title><para>GdvIndicator uses a single CSS node with name indicator.</para>
</refsect2>

</refsect1>
