<refsect1 id="GdvIndicator.property-details" role="property_details">
<title role="property_details.title">Property Details</title>
<refsect2 id="GdvIndicator--rotate-widget-with-axis" role="property"><title>The <literal>“rotate-widget-with-axis”</literal> property</title>
<indexterm zone="GdvIndicator--rotate-widget-with-axis"><primary>GdvIndicator:rotate-widget-with-axis</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting>  “rotate-widget-with-axis”  <link linkend="gboolean"><type>gboolean</type></link></programlisting>
<para>If possible, rotate the widget along the local axis-slope.</para>
<para>Flags: Read / Write</para>
<para>Default value: FALSE</para>
</refsect2>
<refsect2 id="GdvIndicator--show-in-legend" role="property"><title>The <literal>“show-in-legend”</literal> property</title>
<indexterm zone="GdvIndicator--show-in-legend"><primary>GdvIndicator:show-in-legend</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting>  “show-in-legend”           <link linkend="gboolean"><type>gboolean</type></link></programlisting>
<para>If the indicator should be listed in the legend of the affilliated layer.</para>
<para>Flags: Read / Write</para>
<para>Default value: TRUE</para>
</refsect2>
<refsect2 id="GdvIndicator--show-in-out-of-range" role="property"><title>The <literal>“show-in-out-of-range”</literal> property</title>
<indexterm zone="GdvIndicator--show-in-out-of-range"><primary>GdvIndicator:show-in-out-of-range</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting>  “show-in-out-of-range”     <link linkend="gboolean"><type>gboolean</type></link></programlisting>
<para>If the indicator should be shown even if the value is out of the range of
the assigned axis. In some technical applications and if the indicator value
is more important, than an actual remark, this should be considered.</para>
<para>Flags: Read / Write</para>
<para>Default value: FALSE</para>
</refsect2>
<refsect2 id="GdvIndicator--title" role="property"><title>The <literal>“title”</literal> property</title>
<indexterm zone="GdvIndicator--title"><primary>GdvIndicator:title</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting>  “title”                    <link linkend="gchar"><type>gchar</type></link>&#160;*</programlisting>
<para>The title of an indicator.</para>
<para>This property is pretty useless for the moment.</para>
<para>Flags: Read / Write</para>
<para>Default value: "new indicator"</para>
</refsect2>
<refsect2 id="GdvIndicator--value" role="property"><title>The <literal>“value”</literal> property</title>
<indexterm zone="GdvIndicator--value"><primary>GdvIndicator:value</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting>  “value”                    <link linkend="gdouble"><type>gdouble</type></link></programlisting>
<para>Determines the current value of the indicator.</para><para>Flags: Read / Write</para>
<para>Default value: 0</para>
</refsect2>
<refsect2 id="GdvIndicator--widget" role="property"><title>The <literal>“widget”</literal> property</title>
<indexterm zone="GdvIndicator--widget"><primary>GdvIndicator:widget</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting>  “widget”                   <link linkend="GtkWidget"><type>GtkWidget</type></link>&#160;*</programlisting>
<para>A widget, that should be displayed instead of the indicator.</para>
<para>Flags: Read / Write</para>
</refsect2>
<refsect2 id="GdvIndicator--widget-xalign" role="property"><title>The <literal>“widget-xalign”</literal> property</title>
<indexterm zone="GdvIndicator--widget-xalign"><primary>GdvIndicator:widget-xalign</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting>  “widget-xalign”            <link linkend="gdouble"><type>gdouble</type></link></programlisting>
<para>The horizontal alignment of the widget.</para>
<para>Flags: Read / Write</para>
<para>Default value: 0.5</para>
</refsect2>
<refsect2 id="GdvIndicator--widget-yalign" role="property"><title>The <literal>“widget-yalign”</literal> property</title>
<indexterm zone="GdvIndicator--widget-yalign"><primary>GdvIndicator:widget-yalign</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting>  “widget-yalign”            <link linkend="gdouble"><type>gdouble</type></link></programlisting>
<para>The vertical alignment of the widget.</para>
<para>Flags: Read / Write</para>
<para>Default value: 0.5</para>
</refsect2>

